) {\n            return inputStream.readObject();\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1257, "output": 922, "cacheRead": 12288, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 14467, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777682635764, "responseId": "resp_07bda5b59fbfe0ad0169f548cc173081a1a04165dc77e33a64"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_pEGyUUQwZrJok5rGa4hyIFZC|fc_07bda5b59fbfe0ad0169f548d2bd9c81a1843477a647f7fdcb", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 1798 bytes to tests/src/net.sf.ehcache/ehcache-core/2.4.4/src/test/java/net_sf_ehcache/ehcache_core/ConcurrentHashMapTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777682645578}]}
